@Basket_Host = http://localhost:5204
@Basket_Id = BURAYA_BASKET_ID_YAZIN_veya_ilk_GET_sonrasi_response_header_X-Basket-Id_kullanin

### Sepeti getir (X-Basket-Id yoksa yeni id döner)
GET {{Basket_Host}}/api/basket
X-Basket-Id: {{Basket_Id}}
Accept: application/json

###
### Sepete ürün ekle
POST {{Basket_Host}}/api/basket/items
X-Basket-Id: {{Basket_Id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "productId": "urn:product:1",
  "productName": "Örnek Ürün",
  "inventoryItemId": "inv-1",
  "quantity": 2,
  "unitPrice": 99.99,
  "currency": "TRY"
}

###
### Miktar güncelle
PUT {{Basket_Host}}/api/basket/items/urn:product:1
X-Basket-Id: {{Basket_Id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "quantity": 3
}

###
### Sepetten kaldır
DELETE {{Basket_Host}}/api/basket/items/urn:product:1
X-Basket-Id: {{Basket_Id}}
Accept: application/json

###
### Sepeti temizle
DELETE {{Basket_Host}}/api/basket
X-Basket-Id: {{Basket_Id}}
